{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act16d5_level_act16d5_02_beg","storyGroup":"act16d5","storySort":4,"storyDependence":"act16d5_level_act16d5_01_end","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"WR-2","storyName":"墨魉","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"镇上的说书人煮伞先生盛情款待，炎熔也知晓了不少关于“婆山镇”的故事，但无论如何，都无法和现实里的大炎联系起来。这时，一位来自东国的云游僧搭了话。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act16d5/level_act16d5_02_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act16d5_02","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":2,"next":4,"characters":["说书人","乌有","克洛丝","炎熔","村民","嵯峨"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"dialog","id":2},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_bg_bg_black.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":5},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_138#4","id":6},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$path_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/a001/m_dia_path_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":8,"musicid":0},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":9},{"type":"dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"原来如此，是替朋友寻找亲人，为此不远万里来到大炎，实在令人钦佩。","id":10,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/95/Avg_avg_npc_138-4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"不过，灰齐山，勾吴城？我可从来没有听说过附近有这样的城市......不过这里离天岳倒是不远。兴许是某座不知名的小山头，也有可能。","id":11,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/95/Avg_avg_npc_138-4.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":12},{"type":"character","id":13},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":14},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":15},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1e/Avg_bg_bg_landscape.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":16},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":17},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":18},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_144#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"2","id":19},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"呃？天岳......？","id":20,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/41/Avg_char_455_nothing_1-6.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_144#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"1","id":21},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"麻烦了呀。","id":22,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/44/Avg_avg_npc_144-1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","id":23},{"type":"dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"......抱歉，请问我们现在在大炎的哪里？","id":24,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6a/Avg_char_1011_purgatory_1-1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_138#4","id":25},{"type":"dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"此地在婆山地界，名为婆山镇。","id":26,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/95/Avg_avg_npc_138-4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","focus":"1","id":27},{"type":"move","name":"right","xpos":"30","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":28},{"type":"dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"......？","id":29,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/41/Avg_char_455_nothing_1-6.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":30},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":31},{"type":"character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#3","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","focus":"1","id":32},{"type":"jump","name":"left","power":"20","fadetime":"0.5","block":"false","id":33},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"（没听过，绝对没听过！）","id":34,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/84/Avg_char_455_nothing_1-3.png"},{"type":"character","id":35},{"type":"dialog","id":36},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":37},{"type":"character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_138#4","focus":"1","id":38},{"type":"dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"那、那今年的年份是......？","id":39,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6a/Avg_char_1011_purgatory_1-1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_138#4","focus":"2","id":40},{"type":"dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"今年是景祚七年，如今已过立春，恰逢除夕。","id":41,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/95/Avg_avg_npc_138-4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#3","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","focus":"1","id":42},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"......啊？","id":43,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/84/Avg_char_455_nothing_1-3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#3","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","focus":"2","id":44},{"type":"move","name":"right","xpos":"-30","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":45},{"type":"dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"（小声）景祚？","id":46,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6a/Avg_char_1011_purgatory_1-1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#3","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","focus":"1","id":47},{"type":"move","name":"left","xpos":"30","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":48},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"（小声）恩人呐，不瞒你说，我历史学得不好，但景祚......起码近几百年，都未曾听过这么个年号啊......","id":49,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/84/Avg_char_455_nothing_1-3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#3","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","focus":"2","id":50},{"type":"dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"......","id":51,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6a/Avg_char_1011_purgatory_1-1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#3","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","focus":"1","id":52},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"（小声）咋、咋回事儿啊恩人？难不成咱们这是一推门回到一千年前了？","id":53,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/84/Avg_char_455_nothing_1-3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_144#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#3","focus":"1","id":54},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"（小声）一千年前会有这种园林建筑吗？","id":55,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/44/Avg_avg_npc_144-1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_144#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#3","focus":"2","id":56},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"（小声）那显然不能！莫非是这位煮伞居士信口开河？可我看他文质彬彬的，不至于吧？","id":57,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/84/Avg_char_455_nothing_1-3.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":58},{"type":"character","id":59},{"type":"delay","time":"0.6","id":60},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_138#4","id":61},{"type":"dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"三位英雄，你们帮了忙，就是我的贵客，有什么问题直问便是，大可不用客气。","id":62,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/95/Avg_avg_npc_138-4.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":63},{"type":"character","id":64},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":65},{"type":"character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","id":66},{"type":"dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"......能劳烦您给我们讲述一下这里的风土人情吗？实不相瞒，这里并不是我们一开始的目的地，看来是迷了路，有些茫然。","id":67,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6a/Avg_char_1011_purgatory_1-1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"比如......比如就说说这座城镇？","id":68,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6a/Avg_char_1011_purgatory_1-1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_138#4","id":69},{"type":"dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"啊......婆山镇的来历可就大有说法了。相传七十年前，某个富商家起了一场大火，殃及无数。","id":70,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/95/Avg_avg_npc_138-4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"富商受了惊，打算离开那里，另寻一块风水宝地作为自己颐养天年的地方。","id":71,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/95/Avg_avg_npc_138-4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"在那之后，同镇的人们却在满地灰烬中，找到了一幅古怪的画。","id":72,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/95/Avg_avg_npc_138-4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","id":73},{"type":"dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"......画？","id":74,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6a/Avg_char_1011_purgatory_1-1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_138#4","id":75},{"type":"dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"没错。房屋都烧得一干二净，那幅画却安然无恙，掸去灰烬后，完好如初。","id":76,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/95/Avg_avg_npc_138-4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"富商听说了这幅画的事，掏了大价钱重新买了回来，图个辟火消灾的吉利。","id":77,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/95/Avg_avg_npc_138-4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"富商在新居里，越看这画中风水，越觉得中意。便发动上百家仆，去寻找这画卷中描绘的山水宝地——","id":78,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/95/Avg_avg_npc_138-4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"——于是就到了这里，有了这座镇，有了这园林。","id":79,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/95/Avg_avg_npc_138-4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","id":80},{"type":"dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"......是您的祖辈？","id":81,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6a/Avg_char_1011_purgatory_1-1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_138#4","id":82},{"type":"dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"非也非也，世事无常。几十年前，富商死后，几个儿子都不学无术，散尽家财。","id":83,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/95/Avg_avg_npc_138-4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"正巧我爹因为某些机缘巧合，有一笔闲钱，这才买下了这座园子，定居于此。","id":84,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/95/Avg_avg_npc_138-4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"之后，因为这附近少有天灾，山川秀美，吸引了不少风流雅士，久而久之，婆山镇就有了今天这般规模。","id":85,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/95/Avg_avg_npc_138-4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_144#1","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","focus":"1","id":86},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"（听上去真奇妙呢。）","id":87,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/44/Avg_avg_npc_144-1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_144#1","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","focus":"2","id":88},{"type":"dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"（好像没有什么问题......）","id":89,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6a/Avg_char_1011_purgatory_1-1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","id":90},{"type":"dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"那，这天色......？","id":91,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6a/Avg_char_1011_purgatory_1-1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_138#4","id":92},{"type":"dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"天色？","id":93,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/95/Avg_avg_npc_138-4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","id":94},{"type":"dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"呃，就是，白天和黑夜好像混在一起了......","id":95,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6a/Avg_char_1011_purgatory_1-1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_138#4","id":96},{"type":"dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"我们素来日出而作，日落而息，几位有何疑虑？","id":97,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/95/Avg_avg_npc_138-4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","id":98},{"type":"dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"从钟声响起到现在，两个小时......差不多有一个时辰了。太阳的位置从来没有变化过，这是什么原因？","id":99,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6a/Avg_char_1011_purgatory_1-1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_138#1","id":100},{"type":"dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"太阳？变化？","id":101,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/45/Avg_avg_npc_138-1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"日月悬空，日在东，月在西，千古不易，变换什么位置？","id":102,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/45/Avg_avg_npc_138-1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"嗯？各位怎么露出这副脸色？我说了什么不妥当的话吗？","id":103,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/45/Avg_avg_npc_138-1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#3","id":104},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"欸，恩人，打断一下，打断一下啊。","id":105,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/84/Avg_char_455_nothing_1-3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","name2":"avg_npc_138#4","focus":"1","id":106},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"敢问先生明天是不是也会在这里说书？","id":107,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/41/Avg_char_455_nothing_1-6.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","name2":"avg_npc_138#4","focus":"2","id":108},{"type":"dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"那自然。","id":109,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/95/Avg_avg_npc_138-4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","name2":"avg_npc_138#4","focus":"1","id":110},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"既然明天如此，那想必昨天也是这一把折扇，一块醒木？","id":111,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/41/Avg_char_455_nothing_1-6.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","name2":"avg_npc_138#4","focus":"2","id":112},{"type":"dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"赋闲在家，只有收集怪书这一个癖好，只靠说书打发时间。故而每日申时，雷打不动。","id":113,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/95/Avg_avg_npc_138-4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","name2":"avg_npc_138#4","focus":"1","id":114},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"欸，那这日月恒定不落，“今天明天昨天”，这“一天”，要怎么定义？","id":115,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/41/Avg_char_455_nothing_1-6.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","name2":"avg_npc_138#4","focus":"2","id":116},{"type":"dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"乌兄真有意思，十二个时辰为一天，这还用问吗？","id":117,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/95/Avg_avg_npc_138-4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","name2":"avg_npc_138#4","focus":"1","id":118},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"呃......十二时辰，二十四小时，指的不是一昼夜的时间吗？","id":119,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/41/Avg_char_455_nothing_1-6.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","name2":"avg_npc_138#4","focus":"2","id":120},{"type":"dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"噫，奇了怪哉，几位究竟是从何处而来的？十二时辰，指的是从极东日出之地，到极西月出之山之间所需的时间呀？","id":121,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/95/Avg_avg_npc_138-4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"当然，也指这段路途的路段划分，婆山镇自东到西，便是由巳到亥。","id":122,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/95/Avg_avg_npc_138-4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"我听说山外有山，难道鸿洞山外，东升河下，其他的地方不是如此？","id":123,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/95/Avg_avg_npc_138-4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#3","name2":"avg_npc_138#4","focus":"1","id":124},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"这......光是一个婆山镇就占了这么大地盘，其他地方要是有镇子，不得永无天日啊？","id":125,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/84/Avg_char_455_nothing_1-3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_144#1","id":126},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"或者永远是白天，睡觉都睡不好呢，真糟糕。","id":127,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/44/Avg_avg_npc_144-1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_138#1","id":128},{"type":"dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"这......这我还真不清楚。","id":129,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/45/Avg_avg_npc_138-1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","id":130},{"type":"dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"你从没有离开过镇子吗？这里没有其他游客？","id":131,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6a/Avg_char_1011_purgatory_1-1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_138#4","id":132},{"type":"dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"从来没有。很少有人来这里，而离开这里的年轻人，也很少回来。","id":133,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/95/Avg_avg_npc_138-4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"不瞒几位，我们如今所知道的“大炎”，也不过是从富商留下的一些藏书中获悉的罢了。","id":134,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/95/Avg_avg_npc_138-4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","id":135},{"type":"dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"......这里没有遭遇过天灾？","id":136,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6a/Avg_char_1011_purgatory_1-1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_138#4","id":137},{"type":"dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"同样极少。除了典籍记载，至少我们这三代人，从未见过。","id":138,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/95/Avg_avg_npc_138-4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"正因此，我们从不轻易离开婆山镇地界。也正如你所见，来此地的游客都寥寥无几，更别提官差和信使一类的人物。","id":139,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/95/Avg_avg_npc_138-4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"说如今的婆山镇与世隔绝，丝毫不为过。只不过，也唯有不问世事，方能惬意。","id":140,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/95/Avg_avg_npc_138-4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","focus":"1","id":141},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"......","id":142,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/41/Avg_char_455_nothing_1-6.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","focus":"2","id":143},{"type":"dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"那些怪物？","id":144,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6a/Avg_char_1011_purgatory_1-1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_138#2","id":145},{"type":"dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"唉......不知从何时开始，每逢除夕前后，鸿洞山里时常会有些妖物来骚扰城镇，大概三五天时间，这么多年了，一直如此。","id":146,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6b/Avg_avg_npc_138-2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"这些年，我翻遍典籍，问遍了那少之又少的外乡人，从未找到解决之法......","id":147,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6b/Avg_avg_npc_138-2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_138#1","id":148},{"type":"dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"不过只要躲到有太阳的地方，那些妖物就不敢靠近。","id":149,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/45/Avg_avg_npc_138-1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"与其冒着风险去和那些怪物拼个你死我活，不如求个平平安安，躲在太阳底下，不过一夜不眠而已......","id":150,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/45/Avg_avg_npc_138-1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"久而久之，就成了我们这里的习惯。","id":151,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/45/Avg_avg_npc_138-1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#3","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","focus":"1","id":152},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"唉！我还以为这里当真是世外桃源，居然还会有这种麻烦事......那些怪物，太过恐怖，不主动靠近，是明智之举啊！","id":153,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/84/Avg_char_455_nothing_1-3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"（小声）恩人呐，这听着也太邪门了......","id":154,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/84/Avg_char_455_nothing_1-3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#3","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","focus":"2","id":155},{"type":"dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"......先生，这是最后一个请求。","id":156,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6a/Avg_char_1011_purgatory_1-1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","id":157},{"type":"dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"您也知道我们来这里，是来找人的。我这里有一件，呃，信物，您见过吗？","id":158,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6a/Avg_char_1011_purgatory_1-1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":159},{"type":"dialog","id":160},{"type":"showitem","image":"item_act16_1","fadestyle":"horiz_expand_center","fadetime":"0.5","offsetx":"0","width":"200","id":161},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":162},{"type":"hideitem","fadetime":"0.5","id":163},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":164},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_138#1","id":165},{"type":"dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"这......？","id":166,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/45/Avg_avg_npc_138-1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"唔......","id":167,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/45/Avg_avg_npc_138-1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"......巧夺天工啊。","id":168,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/45/Avg_avg_npc_138-1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_138#2","id":169},{"type":"dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"但是......很遗憾，如此非凡的物件，我若是见过，一定——","id":170,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6b/Avg_avg_npc_138-2.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":171},{"type":"character","id":172},{"type":"delay","time":"0.6","id":173},{"type":"playsound","key":"$doorknockquite","volume":"1","id":174},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":175},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":176},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_140#2","fadetime":"1","id":177},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":178},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村民","text":"先生，宴席已经备好了。","id":179,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_140-2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_138#4","id":180},{"type":"dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"好，好，请问几位在镇上可有住处？","id":181,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/95/Avg_avg_npc_138-4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","id":182},{"type":"dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"暂时没有......","id":183,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6a/Avg_char_1011_purgatory_1-1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_138#4","id":184},{"type":"dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"来者是客，不如就在这里歇息一段时日，等除夕过了，再赶路不迟！","id":185,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/95/Avg_avg_npc_138-4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","focus":"1","id":186},{"type":"move","name":"left","xpos":"30","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":187},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"（小声）恩人，您看？","id":188,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/41/Avg_char_455_nothing_1-6.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","focus":"2","id":189},{"type":"move","name":"right","xpos":"-30","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":190},{"type":"dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"（小声）反正也没地方去......不如留在镇子上收集情报。","id":191,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6a/Avg_char_1011_purgatory_1-1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"（小声）这里显然和我们知道的“大炎”有很多不同的地方，以及，我们是怎么到这里来的，还是没有头绪......","id":192,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6a/Avg_char_1011_purgatory_1-1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#4","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","focus":"1","id":193},{"type":"jump","name":"left","power":"20","fadetime":"1","block":"false","id":194},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"好！","id":195,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/50/Avg_char_455_nothing_1-4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"那咱们就，恭敬不如从命啦。","id":196,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/50/Avg_char_455_nothing_1-4.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":197},{"type":"character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#4","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","id":198},{"type":"dialog","id":199},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":200},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":201},{"type":"character","id":202},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7a/Avg_bg_bg_indoor.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":203},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_144#1","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","id":204},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":205},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":206},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":207},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_144#1","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","focus":"1","id":208},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"到头来还是没有任何线索......不过这里的茶闻着好香，这是大炎的绿茶吗？","id":209,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/44/Avg_avg_npc_144-1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_144#1","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","focus":"2","id":210},{"type":"dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"......克洛丝！","id":211,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6a/Avg_char_1011_purgatory_1-1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_144#1","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","focus":"1","id":212},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"没关系啦，我有分寸。","id":213,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/44/Avg_avg_npc_144-1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":214},{"type":"jump","name":"left","power":"20","times":"1","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":215},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"——","id":216,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/44/Avg_avg_npc_144-1.png"},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":217},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"能喝。","id":218,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/44/Avg_avg_npc_144-1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","id":219},{"type":"dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"放在这儿的水果......","id":220,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6a/Avg_char_1011_purgatory_1-1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#4","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","focus":"1","id":221},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"啊，恩人是要试毒？早说啊，我来我来！","id":222,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/50/Avg_char_455_nothing_1-4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#4","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","focus":"2","id":223},{"type":"dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"喂......！","id":224,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6a/Avg_char_1011_purgatory_1-1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#4","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","id":225},{"type":"jump","name":"left","power":"20","times":"2","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":226},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"呜唔！","id":227,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/50/Avg_char_455_nothing_1-4.png"},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":228},{"type":"jump","name":"left","power":"20","times":"2","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":229},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":230},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"嗯，恩人呐，这水果可水灵了，还怪甜的。","id":231,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/50/Avg_char_455_nothing_1-4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#4","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","focus":"2","id":232},{"type":"dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"我不是那个意思......","id":233,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6a/Avg_char_1011_purgatory_1-1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","focus":"1","id":234},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"没有的事！俗话说得好，防人之心不可无嘛。","id":235,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/41/Avg_char_455_nothing_1-6.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","focus":"2","id":236},{"type":"dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"倒不是担心他们下毒......只是逐步确认......我们四周的一切。","id":237,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6a/Avg_char_1011_purgatory_1-1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_144#1","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","focus":"1","id":238},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"其实你还挺烦躁的，对吧？没关系，大家都一样，一头雾水。","id":239,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/44/Avg_avg_npc_144-1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"就像是重新确认自己是不是还活着似的。","id":240,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/44/Avg_avg_npc_144-1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","id":241},{"type":"dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"......重新确认吗。","id":242,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6a/Avg_char_1011_purgatory_1-1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":243},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":244},{"type":"dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"你们在这里休息吧，我还是要去外面看看。","id":245,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6a/Avg_char_1011_purgatory_1-1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_144#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"2","id":246},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"怎么能让恩人独自劳累呢！我毕竟陪您一起去！","id":247,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/41/Avg_char_455_nothing_1-6.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_144#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"1","id":248},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"那我们就分头行动吧，现在这个情况，谁都坐不住呀。","id":249,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/44/Avg_avg_npc_144-1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_144#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"2","id":250},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"好嘞，那咱们......一个时辰后见？","id":251,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/41/Avg_char_455_nothing_1-6.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","id":252},{"type":"dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"好。","id":253,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6a/Avg_char_1011_purgatory_1-1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":254},{"type":"character","id":255},{"type":"character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","id":256},{"type":"delay","time":"0.7","id":257},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"1","id":258},{"type":"character","fadetime":"1","id":259},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":260},{"type":"character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_144#1","focus":"1","id":261},{"type":"dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"......","id":262,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6a/Avg_char_1011_purgatory_1-1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"你觉得他可信吗？","id":263,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6a/Avg_char_1011_purgatory_1-1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_144#1","focus":"2","id":264},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"......虽然在荒野上遇见落难者也不是什么稀罕事，不过巧合这种东西，是最不值得相信的啦。","id":265,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/44/Avg_avg_npc_144-1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_144#1","focus":"1","id":266},{"type":"dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"我想也是，而且他欺骗我们也是事实。","id":267,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6a/Avg_char_1011_purgatory_1-1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"离巢的钳兽是极具攻击性的。虽然我们找到他的时候，他趴在树枝上一副悲惨样......但是那里离车祸地点有足足八百米。","id":268,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6a/Avg_char_1011_purgatory_1-1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"而且看他的动作......","id":269,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6a/Avg_char_1011_purgatory_1-1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_144#1","focus":"2","id":270},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"就算没有恶意，总是要互相保留一些的嘛。","id":271,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/44/Avg_avg_npc_144-1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"......我会稍微留意点的。","id":272,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/44/Avg_avg_npc_144-1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":273},{"type":"dialog","id":274},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":275},{"type":"character","id":276},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/af/Avg_bg_bg_town.png","xSclae":"1.4","yScale":"1.4","id":277},{"type":"character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#2","name2":"char_362_Saga#1","id":278},{"type":"move","name":"right","xpos":"800","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":279},{"type":"move","name":"left","xpos":"-800","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":280},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":281},{"type":"backgroundtween","xFrom":"80","xTo":"-70","duration":"10","block":"false","id":282},{"type":"move","name":"left","xpos":"800","fadetime":"10","block":"false","id":283},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","channel":"bgs","loop":"true","id":284},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":285},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":286},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":287},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"......唉。","id":288,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9b/Avg_char_455_nothing_1-2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"（虽说突然被卷入了莫名怪事......但也算是因祸得福......）","id":289,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9b/Avg_char_455_nothing_1-2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"（话说回来，这可真——不是闹着玩的啊......要是找不到回去的办法，可咋整......）","id":290,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9b/Avg_char_455_nothing_1-2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"（唔......但炎熔和克洛丝确实有恩于我，这事儿也不能赖她们......唉！走一步看一步吧——）","id":291,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9b/Avg_char_455_nothing_1-2.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":292},{"type":"move","name":"right","xpos":"-1000","fadetime":"2.5","block":"false","id":293},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":294},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"bgs","id":295},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"20","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":296},{"type":"move","name":"left","xpos":"-50","fadetime":"0.7","block":"false","id":297},{"type":"move","name":"right","xpos":"50","fadetime":"0.7","block":"false","id":298},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":299},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"20","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":300},{"type":"character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","name2":"char_362_Saga#1","focus":"1","id":301},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"哦哦，抱歉抱歉，实在抱歉，看我一直想事情，一时间都没注意前面——","id":302,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/41/Avg_char_455_nothing_1-6.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","name2":"char_362_Saga#3","focus":"2","id":303},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"20","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":304},{"type":"dialogue","name":"嵯峨","text":"......啊！","id":305},{"type":"dialogue","name":"嵯峨","text":"你看着面生，想必是外边来的吧？小僧已经很久没见过外来客啦！","id":306},{"type":"dialogue","name":"嵯峨","text":"小僧名叫嵯峨，是来自东国的云游僧！敢问施主从何处来？","id":307},{"type":"dialog","id":308},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":309},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":310},{"type":"character","id":311},{"type":"image","id":312}],"characters":["说书人","乌有","克洛丝","炎熔","村民","嵯峨"]}